  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember when, later on, when I went into  the American Arm and I was in basic training, and there were guys who were bitching about the toughness of our basic training.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was laughing inside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I thought, little do they know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And had new, I had learned a minimum of survival, which they had never experienced.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were spoiled kids.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I had been taught the hard way this lesson that I think stayed with me all through my life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 13 SECONDS] In, in, when you, when you asked me before, did I experience anti-Semitism, in, in August, 1934, after I had passed my final examinations and graduated-- by the way, with a certificate of excellence from the European Fashion Academy-- was the only student there and the only Jew who got this, some Nazis who were in our workshop and tried to sabotage me any-- in many, many different ways-- did not get it.",
      "word_count": 77
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is a little bit fitting in with what I said just a few moments ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I, I got a job in Hamburg with one of the fine tailoring firms in Hamburg, [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Christian ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer. ?] And I started with them on the first of August, 1934.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the business manager of this firm was a Nazi, a uniformed Nazi.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the designer I worked for was an SS  man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Piotrowski was his name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We used to call him Pios.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And Piotrowski, after I started there, and I went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer-- ?] his name was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Christian ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Ohlmeyer, ?] who was a friend of my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I got this job partly because of this interrelationship between people who own businesses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And, And I went to Mr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
